The NEWS file for the lwlogger package.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
v0.7.0 -- 03/06/2017

Changes:
Timestamp Precision. Added a tenth-second field to the log timestamp
                     when logging GPIO events.

Scripting Support.  Added support for executing a script in response to
                    GPIO events.

Watchdogs.  Added support for setting a watchdog timer on each GPIO event,
            with the ability to write a log entry or run a script when such
            timer expires.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
